{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"19602a27a0","title":"王延春和赵辛初对湖北麻城县有关粮食调拨问题的意见","origin":"湖北省某档案馆","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"f8f5272cd0","index":0,"year":1959,"month":4,"day":null,"articleId":"19602a27a0"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-dayuejin","name":"中国大跃进-大饥荒数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"682a7f7a09","name":"王德智"},{"id":"a074af2c99","name":"中共湖北省委书记处书记"},{"id":"bdd35156f5","name":"赵辛初"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-dayuejin":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"bd8ca16758","type":"title","text":"王延春和赵辛初对湖北麻城县有关粮食调拨问题的意见","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"19602a27a0"},{"id":"5c35876f74","type":"authors","text":"中共湖北省委书记处书记王延春赵辛初","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"19602a27a0"},{"id":"ff13bc640c","type":"subtitle","text":"(王延春：中共湖北省委副书记；赵辛初：湖北省委书记处书记、副省长)","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"19602a27a0"},{"id":"ca56a62a27","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）关于粮食问题的三个意见","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"19602a27a0"},{"id":"783d5420c7","type":"paragraph","text":"（1）公社化以后，公社管理区调拨的粮食不算购粮任务是不合理，对于公社和小队的压力很大。应以小队为单位算账，调出的算调出单位的征购任务，调进的算供应指标。这样算了以后，完成任务就完成任务了。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"19602a27a0"},{"id":"18cc86b728","type":"paragraph","text":"（2）有些队任务太大，把粮食都拿出来了也完不成任务，应当减下来，不要叫他背没完成任务的包袱。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"19602a27a0"},{"id":"702351e6bd","type":"paragraph","text":"（3）超额完成征购任务的生产队，不论过去和现在，一律加5%的奖金。社员个人卖粮，一律加5%的奖金。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"19602a27a0"},{"id":"527af9f26c","type":"paragraph","text":"（二）关于五级干部会议的时间问题：4月8号、9号、10号以前，结束都可以。在会议期间，有些具体问题，解决不深不透就算了。主要的思想问题，政策问题，解决彻底。强调一条，散会议后，各公社回去以后要继续搞算账，搞兑现，发动群众。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"19602a27a0"},{"id":"f58caa976f","type":"paragraph","text":"(赵)辛初同志两条意见：","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"19602a27a0"},{"id":"d8fd49bf7c","type":"paragraph","text":"1.会上突出抓好超产奖。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"19602a27a0"},{"id":"f40ff7be22","type":"paragraph","text":"2.安排好口粮。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"19602a27a0"}],"page":{"id":"a96923dd97","publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"19602a27a0","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}